    "The first stage, 𝐻 0, produces an initial ranking list retrieved by a simple traditional model for the entire corpus.",
    "The second stage, 𝐻 1, monoBERT, serves as a reranker to obtain a more precise ranking.",
    "In the third stage, duoBERT adopts pairwise learning to further enhance the quality of the ranking list.",
